videos.description: Miami's Kamari Murphy uses a nice bounce pass to set up Bruce Brown for a dunk.
videos.headline: Murphy finds Brown for two-handed slam

videos.description: North Carolina's Joel Berry II starts a fast break with a steal and finds Theo Pinson for the dunk.
videos.headline: Berry feeds Pinson for fast-break dunk

videos.description: Miami's Anthony Lawrence gets a steal and finds Bruce Brown up court who just beats the halftime buzzer with a dunk.
videos.headline: Miami beats the buzzer with a dunk

videos.description: Miami head coach Jim Larranaga discusses his team's play in the closing minutes of the 1st half and defensive adjustments for the 2nd half.
videos.headline: Larranaga on Miami's run to end 1st half

videos.description: North Carolina's Isaiah Hicks scores with two straight dunks.
videos.headline: Hicks throws down a pair of dunks for the Tar Heels

videos.description: Theo Pinson's alley-oop pass for North Carolina inadvertently goes in for a three-point shot.
videos.headline: Missed alley-oop turns into 3-pointer
